lig \u00e5 sitte mye. Det er noe \u00e5 tenke over litt mer. Vi har alle bruke heve-senke pulter p\u00e5 jobben. Jeg m\u00e5 bli flinkere til \u00e5 bruke den."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "39259f97593869928df0ce3e01964eb9a2efc2c9df3c50f27f68aae64c5f3cad"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-10-14T20:38:39.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "For hver time du sitter p\u00e5 rumpa daglig, \u00f8ker risikofaktorene for hjertesykdom med fem prosent."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article11888509.ece/epiphj/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Leikny_Stillesitting071.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/f739509e39e64c86f63ba7063e7ad5013c0a1b57.jpg?58d79395"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Risikoen for hjertesykdom \u00f8ker med hver time sitting -adressa.no", "Krever intensitet", "Alt som f\u00e5r pulsen i v\u00e6ret", "- Sitt mindre", "Sitter i 14 timer", "Trener hardere"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "f739509e39e64c86f63ba7063e7ad5013c0a1b57"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["NTNU", "Oppdraget St. Olavs Hospital", "Overvekt"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "NTNU,Oppdraget St. Olavs Hospital,Overvekt"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["sitte", "lange dager", "\u00f8kte risikoen", "trene"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["javaid nauman", "verdens", "arntzen de besche", "bymarka", "helseunders\u00f8kelsen", "hunt 3", "jebsen senter", "k. g. jebsen senter"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["nord-tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["ulrik wisl\u00f8ff", "kristin wist"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "val